message.content:
1. An intention to treat analysis was conducted.
2. The rate of early treatment failure was high in all three groups.
3. The early treatment failure rate for the AS+AQ group was 13.3%.
4. The early treatment failure rate for the AL group was 15.2%.
5. The early treatment failure rate for the AS+CD group was 9.3%.
6. The primary reason for the high rate of early treatment failure was vomiting.
7. The p-value of the analysis was 0.2.
